text: Andrzej Stalmach was a athlete from Poland. Stalmach competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. He was born on 1 May 1942 and died on 14 September 2020.Andrzej Stalmach == References == Category:1942 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish long jumpers Category:Olympians for Poland
